	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If the problem you have with Visual Studio is the compiler, you should know that you can set up your project to use a different compiler (or linker). It can still be an effective IDE and debugger, even if you can't use its compiler for whatever reason (C99 extension compliance?).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
